1.修改内核配置选项
	Device drivers -->
		[*] Pulse-Width Modulation(PWM) Support -->
			[] JZ PWM driver

2. pwm通道配置
修改Makefie，默认打开PWM0,如要打开多路，打开对应的宏即可;
注意：T10 T20,只有0~3 通道；T30 有 0~7 通道。
DEFS += -DCONFIG_PWM0
#DEFS += -DCONFIG_PWM1
#DEFS += -DCONFIG_PWM2
#DEFS += -DCONFIG_PWM3
#DEFS += -DCONFIG_PWM4
#DEFS += -DCONFIG_PWM5
#DEFS += -DCONFIG_PWM6
#DEFS += -DCONFIG_PWM7

2. KO加载
直接make，会生成sample_pwm_core.ko和sample_pwm_hal.ko,先加载sample_pwm_core.ko，后加载sample_pwm_hal.ko;
